---
import { LINKS, RELEASE } from '../config';

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-white/5 bg-primary">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-sm">
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-2.5" aria-label="Staple ana sayfa">
          <img
            src="/staple-icon.png"
            alt="Staple logosu"
            width="36"
            height="36"
            class="h-9 w-9 rounded-lg"
          />
          <span class="text-lg font-extrabold text-ink-bright">Staple</span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink">
          Toplulukların, arkadaşların ve sohbetlerin tek çatı altında. Konuş,
          sesli takıl, ekran paylaş — hepsini tek yere zımbala.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav
        class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3"
        aria-label="Alt menü"
      >
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-bright">
            Ürün
          </h3>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <li>
              <a href="#ozellikler" class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold"
                >Özellikler</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#indir" class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold"
                >İndir</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#ekranlar" class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold"
                >Ekranlar</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-bright">
            Bağlantılar
          </h3>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <li>
              <a
                href={LINKS.WEB_APP_URL}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold">Web’de Aç</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href={LINKS.GITHUB_URL}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold">GitHub</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href={LINKS.PRIVACY_URL} class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold"
                >Gizlilik</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-bright">
            Destek
          </h3>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <li>
              <a href="#sss" class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold">SSS</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href={LINKS.GITHUB_RELEASES_URL}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                class="text-ink transition-colors hover:text-gold">Sürümler</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-3 border-t border-white/5 pt-6 text-sm text-ink/70 sm:flex-row"
    >
      <p>© {year} Staple. Tüm hakları saklıdır.</p>
      <p>Sürüm {RELEASE.version}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
